00:32:29,390 --> 00:32:30,990
So you drove him away?

572
00:32:32,640 --> 00:32:35,010
I was the one who got driven away.

573
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:40,390
But I fought my way back later.

574
00:32:40,870 --> 00:32:41,790
I have to say,

575
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:43,260
that old guy's swordsmanship

576
00:32:43,290 --> 00:32:44,940
was truly terrifying.

577
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:46,910
I was fortunate enough to break through my limitations,

578
00:32:46,950 --> 00:32:48,470
and a big part of the reason

579
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:50,430
was because I defeated him

580
00:32:50,450 --> 00:32:52,060
and got rid of that frustration.

581
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:54,110
Later, I fought with him for several years.

582
00:32:54,150 --> 00:32:55,230
I had a sudden enlightenment.

583
00:32:55,260 --> 00:32:57,290
When I faced the heavenly tribulation after that,

584
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:58,510
I obtained divine abilities.

585
00:32:58,830 --> 00:33:01,260
My own cultivation also greatly increased.

586
00:33:01,950 --> 00:33:02,750
So...

587
00:33:03,630 --> 00:33:05,020
You defeated him!

588
00:33:05,790 --> 00:33:06,590
No.

589
00:33:07,430 --> 00:33:08,910
But if you think about it, I didn't lose either.

590
00:33:09,390 --> 00:33:10,310
This seems to have had quite an impact

591
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:10,870
on that old fellow.

592
00:33:10,870 --> 00:33:12,110
He never came back after that.

593
00:33:12,990 --> 00:33:14,510
Then why do you seem

594
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:16,870
so resentful whenever you see him?

595
00:33:16,870 --> 00:33:18,470
Because he looks down on me.

596
00:33:21,070 --> 00:33:22,500
Now that you mention it,

597
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:23,430
I feel like he seems to

598
00:33:23,430 --> 00:33:24,670
look down on me too.

599
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,920
He does look down on you.

600
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:27,910
Where's Yuanzhong?

601
00:33:28,630 --> 00:33:29,670
He went back to his room to sleep.

602
00:33:30,470 --> 00:33:31,300
Ji Tanyin has gone off

603
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:32,510
to curry favor with someone else.

604
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:33,630
How can he still sleep?

605
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:18,469
Have some water.

606
00:34:26,150 --> 00:34:27,909
Ji Tanyin and her master

607
00:34:27,909 --> 00:34:29,170
talked all night.

608
00:34:31,310 --> 00:34:32,830
The master and student reunited.

609
00:34:32,830 --> 00:34:35,550
It's normal to have a long conversation by candlelight, isn't it?

610
00:34:35,630 --> 00:34:37,469
Although it's a master-student relationship,

611
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:41,110
they're still a man and woman alone together.

612
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:52,960
I want to eat milk cake for breakfast.

613
00:34:55,500 --> 00:34:56,270
You know

614
00:34:56,270 --> 00:34:57,590
I only know how to make soy milk.

615
00:34:57,590 --> 00:34:58,830
Would soy milk and steamed buns be okay?

616
00:34:59,390 --> 00:35:00,880
I also want to eat lotus flower with blood duck

617
00:35:01,130 --> 00:35:02,130
and drink soft-shelled turtle soup.

618
00:35:02,910 --> 00:35:04,230
I don't know how to make those either.

619
00:35:04,630 --> 00:35:05,750
Ji Tanyin can make them.

620
00:35:06,170 --> 00:35:06,970
Go ask her.

621
00:35:07,430 --> 00:35:09,230
Are you sure she can?

622
00:35:09,390 --> 00:35:10,860
She's a quick learner.

623
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:26,470
Master.

624
00:35:27,350 --> 00:35:28,150
I don't dare to accept such a title.

625
00:35:28,740 --> 00:35:30,330
You are already a god.

626
00:35:30,410 --> 00:35:31,730
while I am just a mortal.

627
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:33,350
I can't be your master anymore.

628
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,500
Once a master, always a master.

629
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:38,990
I will always remember

630
00:35:38,990 --> 00:35:40,430
the kindness of your teachings.

631
00:35:40,910 --> 00:35:41,670
The reason I have

632
00:35:41,670 --> 00:35:42,990
achieved what I have today

633
00:35:42,990 --> 00:35:43,510
is all because of

634
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:45,060
your constant guidance

635
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:46,140
and generous teachings.

636
00:35:46,390 --> 00:35:47,470
Without your kindness,

637
00:35:47,490 --> 00:35:48,930
how can I be where I am today?

638
00:35:55,590 --> 00:35:57,350
Are you angry with me, Master?

639
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:05,660
I left without saying goodbye back then.

640
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:08,240
It was indeed my fault.

641
00:36:08,710 --> 00:36:09,590
It was because…

642
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:15,430
Because the process

643
00:36:15,430 --> 00:36:16,690
was just too sudden.

644
00:36:16,710 --> 00:36:18,100
I ascended to heaven in an instant.

645
00:36:18,270 --> 00:36:18,910
I really

646
00:36:18,910 --> 00:36:20,230
had no preparation at all.

647
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:22,230
You know me, Master.

648
00:36:22,310 --> 00:36:23,670
If I had known beforehand

649
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:25,140
that I would have such good fortune,

650
00:36:25,390 --> 00:36:26,190
how could I not have

651
00:36:26,190 --> 00:36:27,630
informed you in advance?

652
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:36,070
You made a heavenly oath?

653
00:36:38,350 --> 00:36:39,390
If you break that oath,

654
00:36:39,590 --> 00:36:40,910
you will die.

655
00:36:41,310 --> 00:36:42,830
Then I just won't break it.

656
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,180
Stand up and speak.

657
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,170
Thank you, Master.

658
00:37:10,550 --> 00:37:11,750
Please have some tea, Master.

659
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:17,990
How have you been these past few years, Master?

660
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:18,950
Getting by.

661
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:22,110
Before I knew it,

662
00:37:22,130 --> 00:37:23,860
over a thousand years have passed.

663
00:37:24,310 --> 00:37:25,190
I never imagined

664
00:37:25,190 --> 00:37:26,710
I would meet you again, Master.

665
00:37:28,630 --> 00:37:29,750
You mean you didn't expect

666
00:37:30,390 --> 00:37:31,550
that I'd still be alive, right?

667
00:37:31,950 --> 00:37:32,870
No, that's not it.

668
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,630
Of course, as your student, I hope

669
00:37:34,630 --> 00:37:35,430
that you will live

670
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:36,750
a long and prosperous life.

671
00:37:37,750 --> 00:37:38,950
When I was there,

672
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:40,780
I often prayed for your well-being.

673
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:44,510
Lies.

674
00:37:45,070 --> 00:37:45,980
It's true.

675
00:37:46,430 --> 00:37:47,630
I truly wished for you

676
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:48,830
to live a long and prosperous life.

677
00:37:49,270 --> 00:37:50,310
Only in this way

678
00:37:50,340 --> 00:37:52,340
could I see you again.

679
00:37:53,130 --> 00:37:53,990
Praying for me?

680
00:37:55,230 --> 00:37:56,030
Often?

681
00:37:57,390 --> 00:37:58,500
Not often,

682
00:37:58,870 --> 00:37:59,660
but

683
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:01,670
I still did it occasionally.

684
00:38:02,110 --> 00:38:03,550
In any case, I've always

685
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:05,030
remembered you in my heart.

686
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:10,310
Master, have you been using a sword recently?

687
00:38:11,310 --> 00:38:12,910
I am now a sword cultivator.

688
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,910
You're not studying craftsmanship anymore?

689
00:38:15,350 --> 00:38:17,630
I'm slow-witted and have made no progress.

690
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:18,430
I've given up on it.

691
00:38:18,430 --> 00:38:19,230
How can that be?

692
00:38:19,790 --> 00:38:20,950
Master, you're knowledgeable in both ancient and modern matters.

693
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:22,030
Your talent is unparalleled

694
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:24,750
and your disciples are spread all over the world.

695
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,360
Even after a thousand years,

696
00:38:26,430 --> 00:38:28,350
your craftsmanship has been passed down to this day.

697
00:38:28,350 --> 00:38:30,060
It's still widely used by many people.

698
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,180
In this world,

699
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:33,850
no one is more skilled than you.

700
00:38:34,870 --> 00:38:35,670
If

701
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,640
I'm really as good as you say,

702
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:41,030
then why are you the God of Craft?

703
00:38:41,990 --> 00:38:42,920
That's because

704
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,150
you don't care about becoming a god.

705
00:38:44,310 --> 00:38:45,950
Since you're my master,

706
00:38:45,950 --> 00:38:46,880
it proves that you

707
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,170
are even more powerful than gods.

708
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:56,070
I didn't expect

709
00:38:56,250 --> 00:38:57,640
for your personality to still be the same

710
00:38:57,680 --> 00:38:58,630
after becoming a god.

711
00:38:59,350 --> 00:39:00,430
Not only that,

712
00:39:00,470 --> 00:39:02,230
my reverence for you

713
00:39:02,230 --> 00:39:03,280
has never changed either.

714
00:39:05,270 --> 00:39:06,950
Are you not content being a god?

715
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:08,070
Why come down to the mortal world?

716
00:39:09,910 --> 00:39:10,620
To find someone.

717
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:11,580
Who?

718
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:13,750
Ji Tanyin.

719
00:39:14,030 --> 00:39:15,390
Yuanzhong wants to have lotus blood duck,

720
00:39:15,390 --> 00:39:16,070
turtle soup,

721
00:39:16,070 --> 00:39:17,190
and also milk cake.

722
00:39:17,390 --> 00:39:18,710
He wants you to prepare breakfast.

723
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:19,630
Got it!

724
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:21,470
I'll go prepare breakfast first.

725
00:39:21,470 --> 00:39:23,100
I'll catch up with you later, Master.

726
00:39:38,890 --> 00:39:40,210
Such a sumptuous breakfast.

727
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:41,720
Miss Ji, thank you for your hard work.

728
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:43,620
It's no trouble. Please, have a seat.

729
00:39:44,250 --> 00:39:45,120
Time to eat!

730
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,550
Please sit down, Master.

731
00:40:14,390 --> 00:40:15,950
According to your past preferences,

732
00:40:15,980 --> 00:40:17,310
I've prepared a few dishes.

733
00:40:17,310 --> 00:40:18,270
I'm not sure if your tastes

734
00:40:18,270 --> 00:40:19,180
have changed.

735
00:40:19,210 --> 00:40:20,330
Please try them.

736
00:40:21,190 --> 00:40:21,990
How impressive.

737
00:40:22,350 --> 00:40:23,310
After all these years,

738
00:40:23,430 --> 00:40:25,360
you still remember my preferences.

739
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:27,500
No matter what,

740
00:40:27,540 --> 00:40:29,150
I'll never forget your preferences.

741
00:40:30,790 --> 00:40:31,440
Eat.

742
00:40:34,470 --> 00:40:35,270
I heard you are

743
00:40:35,270 --> 00:40:36,910
the master of my handmaiden.

744
00:40:36,990 --> 00:40:38,510
May I ask your name?

745
00:40:41,670 --> 00:40:43,070
My master's name is Xie You.

746
00:40:43,070 --> 00:40:44,670
He specializes in the art of craftsmanship.

747
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:46,310
He's the pioneer of mechanical engineering.

748
00:40:46,350 --> 00:40:47,580
He's also skilled in water management,

749
00:40:47,580 --> 00:40:49,150
casting, and creation.

750
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:50,150
He has taught many

751
00:40:50,150 --> 00:40:51,750
renowned master craftsmen.

752
00:40:52,990 --> 00:40:54,710
So, may I ask,

753
00:40:54,710 --> 00:40:56,830
which famous master craftsmen has he taught?

754
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:58,830
There's Yu Wenjing,

755
00:40:58,830 --> 00:40:59,990
who's an expert in hydraulics.

756
00:40:59,990 --> 00:41:01,310
And there's Ma Xian, known for

757
00:41:01,310 --> 00:41:02,310
his water-powered automata.

758
00:41:02,310 --> 00:41:03,760
They are all my master's disciples.

759
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:05,590
I've never heard of any of them.

760
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:08,470
I guess they're not that famous after all.

761
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:11,950
That just shows how ignorant you are.

762
00:41:12,470 --> 00:41:14,110
If you dare call them famous,

763
00:41:14,130 --> 00:41:16,090
then everyone should know their names

764
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:17,120
and their deeds.

765
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,550
I don't know them,

766
00:41:18,550 --> 00:41:21,110
which means they're not that famous yet.

767
00:41:23,700 --> 00:41:25,260
Alright, Yuanzhong.

768
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:26,710
Let's eat.

769
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,250
The soup has such a strong fishy smell.

770
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,510
How can one swallow it?

771
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:46,590
Is it strong?

772
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:48,360
Let me taste it.

773
00:41:51,870 --> 00:41:52,920
It's quite fresh.

774
00:41:53,350 --> 00:41:55,040
Go make me another bowl.

775
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:03,280
Didn't you say you wanted to stay with me?

776
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:04,580
Now I want

777
00:42:04,580 --> 00:42:06,230
a new bowl of soup.

778
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:14,550
You're weak and deficient in qi.

779
00:42:14,700 --> 00:42:16,450
Soft-shelled turtle is very cooling.

780
00:42:16,490 --> 00:42:17,410
If you eat too much,

781
00:42:18,030 --> 00:42:19,300
you'll die even sooner.

782
00:42:20,540 --> 00:42:21,350
As for me,

783
00:42:21,670 --> 00:42:23,310
I have quite a bit of knowledge in medicine.

784
00:42:23,860 --> 00:42:25,030
Observing your appearance,

785
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:26,670
it's like a lamp running out of oil.

786
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:29,400
When your lungs are deficient and you cough a lot,

787
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:31,060
and when you have trouble sleeping and many dreams,

788
00:42:31,790 --> 00:42:34,660
you two can start arranging his funeral.

789
00:42:40,590 --> 00:42:41,930
No need for your concern.

790
00:42:42,540 --> 00:42:44,350
I see you're not young either.

791
00:42:44,620 --> 00:42:46,380
Who knows which of us

792
00:42:46,560 --> 00:42:47,800
will die first?
